name: Medieval Dynasty New Settlement
summary: Traverse vast landscapes of the Green Valley, to uncover all its secrets and build the most prosperous settlement out there! Open world main map filled with interesting places to visit is lively with all the fauna and flora surrounding you. But remember, medieval life can’t be too easy, so be prepared if some obstacles might make your day less peaceful than planned. Play solo or team up with friends and explore the beautiful but harsh medieval world in the Co-Op Mode together.
